snippet.title: JusticeExe - Teaser
snippet.description:
Justice.exe is an rpg of practicing law with interactive elements. Discover facts, build your arguments, and bring the prosecution to its knees in interactive stories of morally ambivalent robots and disembodied AI.

Will you be a silver tongued devil or practice more witness intimidation than law?

Steam Page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1291210/Justiceexe/
